        "zh": "1.概論<br>2.資料型別、運算子與輸出入<br>3.選擇結構<br>4.反覆及迴圈結構<br>5.陣列與字串<br>",
        "en": "1.Introduction<br>2.Data Types, Operator, Input and Output<br>3.Selection Structures<br>4.Repetition and Loop Structures<br>5.Array and String<br>"
